OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 12 JUN
OL,4,CCHANNELS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1995FL!ve TV begins broadcasting.
OL,7,
OL,8,FThe cable-only channel is perhaps
OL,9,Fremembered for its low-brow content,
OL,10,Fsuch as Topless Darts, Tiffany's Big
OL,11,FCity Tips (where model Tiffany Banister
OL,12,Frelayed financial news while stripping
OL,13,Fto her underwear) and News Bunny (where
OL,14,Fa person in a rabbit suit stood behind
OL,15,Fa news presenter, reacting to each
OL,16,Fstory).
OL,17,
OL,18,FThe channel was operated by Mirror
OL,19,FGroup Newspapers. At launch, it was
OL,20,Fheaded by Kelvin MacKenzie, with Janet
OL,21,FStreet-Porter as managing director. It
OL,22,Ffeatured a host of young presenters who
OL,23,Sppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
